oice. He calls his own sheep by name and leads them out. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When he has brought all his own outside, he goes ahead of them. The sheep follow him because they know his voice. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They will never follow a stranger; instead they will run away from him, because they don’t know the voice of strangers.” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Jesus gave them this figure of speech, but they did not understand "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 9:32","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":32,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:50","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":50,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:45","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":45,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 18:34","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":34,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 2:24","book":"Jhn","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":16,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" what he was telling them."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 9:32","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":32},{"label":"Lk 2:50","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":50},{"label":"Lk 9:45","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":45},{"label":"Lk 18:34","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":34},{"label":"Jn 2:24","book":"Jhn","chapter":2,"verse":24},{"label":"Jn 12:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Jesus said again, “Truly I tell you, I am"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 3:14","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 45:8","book":"Psa","chapter":45,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:24","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" the gate for the sheep."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:15","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":15,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 3:14","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":14},{"label":"Ps 45:8","book":"Psa","chapter":45,"verse":8},{"label":"Jn 8:24","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":24},{"label":"Mt 7:15","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"All who came before me"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss omit before me"},{"kind":"text","text":" are thieves and robbers, but the sheep didn’t listen to them. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss omit before me"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am the gate. If anyone enters by me, he will be saved and will come in and go out and find pasture. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"A thief comes only to steal"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:28","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and kill and destroy."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 6:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":27,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" I have come so that they may have life and have it in abundance."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 4:28","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":28},{"label":"Jn 6:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“I am the good shepherd.Ps 23"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 40:11","book":"Isa","chapter":40,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:23","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":23,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 37:24","book":"Ezk","chapter":37,"verse":24,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 13:7","book":"Zec","chapter":13,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 21:15–17","book":"Jhn","chapter":21,"verse":15,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 13:20","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":20,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:25","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":25,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":4,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 7:17","book":"Rev","chapter":7,"verse":17,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" The good shepherd lays down his life for the sheep."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 20:28","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":28,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:45","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":45,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 5:21","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":21,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:13","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:16","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"o"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 40:11","book":"Isa","chapter":40,"verse":11},{"label":"Ezk 34:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":12},{"label":"Ezk 34:23","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":23},{"label":"Ezk 37:24","book":"Ezk","chapter":37,"verse":24},{"label":"Zch 13:7","book":"Zec","chapter":13,"verse":7},{"label":"Jn 21:15–17","book":"Jhn","chapter":21,"verse":15},{"label":"Heb 13:20","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":20},{"label":"1Pt 2:25","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":25},{"label":"1Pt 5:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":4},{"label":"Rv 7:17","book":"Rev","chapter":7,"verse":17},{"label":"Mt 20:28","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":28},{"label":"Mk 10:45","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":45},{"label":"2Co 5:21","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":21},{"label":"Gl 3:13","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":13},{"label":"1Jn 3:16","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The hired hand, since he is not the shepherd and doesn’t own the sheep, leaves them"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit leaves the sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":" and runs away when he sees a wolf"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:3","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" coming. The wolf then snatches and scatters them. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 10:3","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit leaves the sheep"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This happens because he is a hired hand and doesn’t care about the sheep."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“I am the good shepherd. I know my own, and my own know me, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"just as the Father knows me, and I know the Father."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 11:27","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":27,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:22","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" I lay down my life"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 20:28","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":28,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the sheep. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 11:27","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":27},{"label":"Lk 10:22","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":22},{"label":"Mt 20:28","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But I have other sheep"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 56:8","book":"Isa","chapter":56,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:11–13","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:11","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:12","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:32","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":32,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:34–35","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":34,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:25","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":25,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" that are not from this sheep pen; I must bring them also, and they will listen to my voice. Then there will be one flock, one shepherd."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:23","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":23,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 37:24","book":"Ezk","chapter":37,"verse":24,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 11:52","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":52,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:11","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":11,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:20","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":20,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:11–19","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":11,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 56:8","book":"Isa","chapter":56,"verse":8},{"label":"Ezk 34:11–13","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":11},{"label":"Mt 8:11","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":11},{"label":"Mt 8:12","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":12},{"label":"Jn 12:32","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":32},{"label":"Ac 10:34–35","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":34},{"label":"1Pt 2:25","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":25},{"label":"Ezk 34:23","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":23},{"label":"Ezk 37:24","book":"Ezk","chapter":37,"verse":24},{"label":"Jn 11:52","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":52},{"label":"Jn 17:11","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":11},{"label":"Jn 17:20","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":20},{"label":"Eph 2:11–19","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jhn:10:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is why the Father loves me,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:35","book":"Jhn","cha